def blank_as_1(x):
    return when(col(x) == '', 1).otherwise(0) # 1 == alive, 0 == demised for ICD10

def blank_as_null(x):
    return when(col(x) != ' ', col(x)).otherwise(np.nan)

icds = pndf_icd.groupby('ICD10')

for name, groupdf in icds:

        print(name," -- ",groupdf['ICD10'].count())
